#. module: holiday_house
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:holiday_house.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"<strong>In such situation, feel free to experiment with this database and "
"then to create a new one for your own usage.</strong>"
msgstr ""
"<strong>ໃນສະຖານະການແບບນີ້, ຮູ້ສຶກສະບາຍໃຈທີ່ຈະທົດລອງກັບຖານຂໍ້ມູນນີ້ ແລະ ຈາກນັ້ນສ້າງອັນໃໝ່ເພື່ອການນຳ"
"ໃຊ້ຂອງທ່ານເອງ.</strong>"

#. module: holiday_house
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:holiday_house.welcome_article_body
msgid "<strong>Multiple resource blocking / period closure</strong>"
msgstr "<strong>ການປິດກັ້ນຫຼາຍຊັບພະຍາກອນ / ການປິດຊ່ວງເວລາ</strong>"

#. module: holiday_house
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:holiday_house.welcome_article_body
msgid "<strong>Shared offers</strong>"
msgstr "<strong>ຂໍ້ສະເໜີທີ່ໃຊ້ຮ່ວມກັນ</strong>"

#. module: holiday_house
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:holiday_house.welcome_article_body
msgid "<strong>Single resource blocking</strong>"
msgstr "<strong>ການປິດກັ້ນຊັບພະຍາກອນດຽວ</strong>"

#. module: holiday_house
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:holiday_house.welcome_article_body
msgid "<strong>Use case</strong>"
msgstr "<strong>ກໍລະນີການນຳໃຊ້</strong>"

#. module: holiday_house
#: model:product.template,name:holiday_house.product_template_13
msgid "A-frame Cabin"
msgstr "ກະຕູບຊົງເອ (A-frame)"

#. module: holiday_house
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:holiday_house.welcome_article_body
msgid "Access to more details clicking the slot."
msgstr "ເຂົ້າເບິ່ງລາຍລະອຽດເພີ່ມເຕີມໂດຍການຄລິກທີ່ຊ່ອງວ່າງ."

#. module: holiday_house
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:holiday_house.homepage
msgid ""
"Accommodation were exactly what we needed for a family moment.<br/>Many "
"thanks agan."
msgstr ""
"ບ່ອນພັກແມ່ນສິ່ງທີ່ພວກເຮົາຕ້ອງການແທ້ໆສຳລັບຊ່ວງເວລາຂອງຄອບຄົວ.<br/>ຂອບໃຈຫຼາຍໆອີກຄັ້ງ."

#. module: holiday_house
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:holiday_house.welcome_article_body
msgid "Add here as many of them as needed."
msgstr "ເພີ່ມພວກມັນຢູ່ທີ່ນີ້ໄດ້ຫຼາຍເທົ່າທີ່ຕ້ອງການ."

#. module: holiday_house
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:holiday_house.welcome_article_body
msgid "Adjust the number of stars, leave a comment and send it!"
msgstr "ປັບຈຳນວນດາວ, ຂຽນຄຳຄິດເຫັນ ແລະ ສົ່ງມັນເລີຍ!"

#. module: holiday_house
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:holiday_house.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"Adjust the rental dates, click the book button and then proceed to checkout."
msgstr "ປັບປ່ຽນວັນທີເຊົ່າ, ຄລິກປຸ່ມຈອງ ແລະ ຈາກນັ້ນດຳເນີນການໄປທີ່ການຊຳລະເງິນ."

#. module: holiday_house
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:holiday_house.welcome_article_body
msgid "Adjusting your offers in consequence"
msgstr "ປັບປຸງຂໍ້ສະເໜີຂອງທ່ານຕາມຄວາມເໝາະສົມ"

#. module: holiday_house
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:holiday_house.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"Again, the <strong>Holiday House App </strong>helps you manage the end of "
"the stay!"
msgstr ""
"ອີກຄັ້ງໜຶ່ງ, <strong>ແອັບເຮືອນພັກຜ່ອນ (Holiday House App) </strong>ຊ່ວຍໃຫ້ທ່ານຈັດການຊ່ວງທ້າຍ"
"ຂອງການເຂົ້າພັກ!"

#. module: holiday_house
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:holiday_house.custom_product_name
msgid "All Houses"
msgstr "ເຮືອນທັງໝົດ"

#. module: holiday_house
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:holiday_house.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"Alternatively to individual resource blocking slots described earlier, you "
"can select a resource this leave applies to."
msgstr ""
"ນອກເໜືອຈາກການປິດກັ້ນຊັບພະຍາກອນແຕ່ລະອັນທີ່ໄດ້ກ່າວມາກ່ອນໜ້ານີ້, ທ່ານສາມາດເລືອກຊັບພະຍາກອນທີ່ການລານີ້ມີຜົ"
"ນບັງຄັບໃຊ້."

#. module: holiday_house
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:holiday_house.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"Alternatively, switch to the list view, which is more suitable if the "
"booking is not during the visualized date range and update the booking date "
"range."
msgstr ""
"ຫຼື ອີກທາງເລືອກໜຶ່ງ, ປ່ຽນເປັນມຸມມອງລາຍການ, ເຊິ່ງເໝາະສົມກວ່າຖ້າການຈອງບໍ່ໄດ້ຢູ່ໃນຊ່ວງວັນທີທີ່ສະແດງໃຫ້ເຫັ"
"ນ ແລະ ອັບເດດຊ່ວງວັນທີຈອງ."

#. module: holiday_house
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:holiday_house.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"Alternatively, type in the search bar and select the appropriate filter."
msgstr "ຫຼື ອີກທາງເລືອກໜຶ່ງ, ພິມໃສ່ແຖບຄົ້ນຫາ ແລະ ເລືອກຕົວຕອງທີ່ເໝາະສົມ."

#. module: holiday_house
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:holiday_house.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"Alternatively, you can create a slot as placeholder from the planning "
"directly:"
msgstr ""
"ຫຼື ອີກທາງເລືອກໜຶ່ງ, ທ່ານສາມາດສ້າງຊ່ອງວ່າງເພື່ອຈອງໄວ້ກ່ອນຈາກການວາງແຜນໂດຍກົງ:"

#. module: holiday_house
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:holiday_house.homepage
msgid ""
"Amazing stay at the heart of a pine tree forest. Resourcing and peaceful. "
"<br/>Lovely furnished with all the necessary, even including games such as "
"Mölkky. <br/>I can only recommend!"
msgstr ""
"ການເຂົ້າພັກທີ່ໜ້າຕື່ນຕາຕື່ນໃຈຢູ່ໃຈກາງປ່າສົນ. ໄດ້ພັກຜ່ອນ ແລະ ສະຫງົບສຸກ. <br/>ຕົບແຕ່ງຢ່າງໜ້າຮັກດ້ວຍທຸກສິ່ງທີ່"
"ຈຳເປັນ, ແມ້ແຕ່ເກມຕ່າງໆ ເຊັ່ນ Mölkky. <br/>ຂ້ອຍຂໍແນະນຳເລີຍ!"

#. module: holiday_house
#: model_terms:product.template,website_description:holiday_house.product_template_12
#: model_terms:product.template,website_description:holiday_house.product_template_13
#: model_terms:product.template,website_description:holiday_house.product_template_14
msgid "An address must be specified for a map to be embedded"
msgstr "ຕ້ອງລະບຸທີ່ຢູ່ເພື່ອຝັງແຜນທີ່"

#. module: holiday_house
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:holiday_house.welcome_article_body
msgid "An automation is setup for an email to be sent automatically for you."
msgstr "ລະບົບອັດຕະໂນມັດຖືກຕັ້ງຄ່າເພື່ອໃຫ້ອີເມລຖືກສົ່ງອອກໂດຍອັດຕະໂນມັດສຳລັບທ່ານ."

#. module: holiday_house
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:holiday_house.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"Any time you create a new survey and save it with the setting \"is customer satisfaction survey\", previous ones\n"
"                will be archived so that it becomes your new default survey."
msgstr ""
"ທຸກຄັ້ງທີ່ທ່ານສ້າງແບບສຳຫຼວດໃໝ່ ແລະ ບັນທຶກມັນດ້ວຍການຕັ້ງຄ່າ \"ແມ່ນແບບສຳຫຼວດຄວາມພຶງພໍໃຈຂອງລູກຄ້າ\", ອັ"
"ນເກົ່າກ່ອນໜ້ານີ້\n"
"                ຈະຖືກເກັບໄວ້ ເພື່ອໃຫ້ມັນກາຍເປັນແບບສຳຫຼວດເລີ່ມຕົ້ນໃໝ່ຂອງທ່ານ."

#. module: holiday_house
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:holiday_house.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"Anyone can create a portal account on your database.<br/>\n"
"Open your website home page in a private tab to do so."
msgstr ""
"ທຸກຄົນສາມາດສ້າງບັນຊີພໍທັລ (Portal) ໃນຖານຂໍ້ມູນຂອງທ່ານໄດ້.<br/>\n"
"ເປີດໜ້າທຳອິດຂອງເວັບໄຊທ໌ຂອງທ່ານໃນແຖບສ່ວນຕົວເພື່ອເຮັດແບບນັ້ນ."

#. module: holiday_house
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:holiday_house.welcome_article_body
msgid "Assign them a resource, which helps you keeping track."
msgstr "ມອບໝາຍຊັບພະຍາກອນໃຫ້ພວກເຂົາ, ເຊິ່ງຊ່ວຍໃຫ້ທ່ານຕິດຕາມໄດ້ງ່າຍ."

#. module: holiday_house
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:holiday_house.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"At any time from the guest order, use the Send message capability in the "
"chatter to exchange with your guest."
msgstr ""
"ໃນເວລາໃດກໍຕາມຈາກໃບສັ່ງຈອງຂອງແຂກ, ໃຫ້ໃຊ້ຄວາມສາມາດໃນການສົ່ງຂໍ້ຄວາມໃນ Chatter ເພື່ອສື່ສານກັບແຂ"
"ກຂອງທ່ານ."

#. module: holiday_house
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:holiday_house.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"At any time you can adjust the city tax count delivered by re-opening the "
"city tax widget clicking the City Tax button on the guest order."
msgstr ""
"ໃນເວລາໃດກໍຕາມ ທ່ານສາມາດປັບຈຳນວນອາກອນເມືອງທີ່ສົ່ງມອບ ໂດຍການເປີດ widget ອາກອນເມືອງຄືນໃໝ່ ດ້ວ"
"ຍການຄລິກປຸ່ມ City Tax ໃນໃບສັ່ງຈອງຂອງແຂກ."

#. module: holiday_house
#: model:product.template,name:holiday_house.product_template_14
msgid "Beach House"
msgstr "ເຮືອນແຄມທະເລ"

#. module: holiday_house
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:holiday_house.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"Beyond daily operations, the Steering menu serves as the \"Captain’s "
"Bridge\" of your holiday houses. It provides a 500-day horizon to anticipate"
" market trends, manage risks, and optimize your revenue."
msgstr ""
"ນອກເໜືອຈາກການດຳເນີນງານປະຈຳວັນແລ້ວ, ເມນູ Steering ຍັງເຮັດໜ້າທີ່ເປັນ \"ຫ້ອງຄວບຄຸມ\" ຂອງເຮືອນພັ"
"ກຜ່ອນຂອງທ່ານ. ມັນຊ່ວຍໃຫ້ເຫັນພາບລວມ 500 ວັນ ເພື່ອຄາດການແນວໂນ້ມຕະຫຼາດ, ຈັດການຄວາມສ່ຽງ ແລະ ເພີ່"
"ມລາຍຮັບຂອງທ່ານໃຫ້ສູງສຸດ."

#. module: holiday_house
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:holiday_house.welcome_article_body
msgid "Blocking resources"
msgstr "ການປິດກັ້ນຊັບພະຍາກອນ"

#. module: holiday_house
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:holiday_house.welcome_article_body
msgid "Booking a house"
msgstr "ການຈອງເຮືອນ"

#. module: holiday_house
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:holiday_house.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"By uploading this module's demo data, your database has been filled with a "
"few products, sale orders and more."
msgstr ""
"ໂດຍການອັບໂຫຼດຂໍ້ມູນຕົວຢ່າງຂອງໂມດູນນີ້, ຖານຂໍ້ມູນຂອງທ່ານຈະຖືກເຕີມເຕັມດ້ວຍສິນຄ້າບາງຢ່າງ, ໃບສັ່ງຂາຍ ແລ"
"ະ ອື່ນໆ."

#. module: holiday_house
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:holiday_house.welcome_article_body
msgid "Charge your customer for the resulting amount and you're all set!"
msgstr "ເກັບເງິນລູກຄ້າຕາມຈຳນວນທີ່ສະແດງ ແລະ ທ່ານກໍພ້ອມແລ້ວ!"

#. module: holiday_house
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:holiday_house.welcome_article_body
msgid "Charge your guests"
msgstr "ເກັບເງິນແຂກຂອງທ່ານ"

#. module: holiday_house
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:holiday_house.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"Check and adjust if needed the number of guest who stayed in each room. Then"
" confirm the number of city tax to be charged, which updated the delivered "
"city tax count."
msgstr ""
"ກວດສອບ ແລະ ປັບປຸງຖ້າຈຳເປັນກ່ຽວກັບຈຳນວນແຂກທີ່ພັກໃນແຕ່ລະຫ້ອງ. ຈາກນັ້ນຢືນຢັນຈຳນວນອາກອນເມືອງທີ່ຈະເກັ"
"ບ, ເຊິ່ງຈະອັບເດດຈຳນວນອາກອນເມືອງທີ່ສົ່ງມອບ."

#. module: holiday_house
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:holiday_house.welcome_article_body
msgid "Check guests in"
msgstr "ເຊັກອິນແຂກເຂົ້າ"

#. module: holiday_house
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:holiday_house.welcome_article_body
msgid "Check guests out"
msgstr "ເຊັກເອົາແຂກອອກ"

#. module: holiday_house
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:holiday_house.welcome_article_body
msgid "Check the invoice data and confirm it."
msgstr "ກວດສອບຂໍ້ມູນໃບແຈ້ງໜີ້ ແລະ ຢືນຢັນມັນ."

#. module: holiday_house
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:holiday_house.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"City Taxes are to be billed to spent nights in practice and not in theory "
"and are counted as the sum of nights each guest stayed."
msgstr ""
"ອາກອນເມືອງແມ່ນຈະຖືກເກັບຕາມຄືນທີ່ພັກແທ້ໃນທາງປະຕິບັດ ແລະ ບໍ່ແມ່ນໃນທາງທິດສະດີ ແລະ ຖືກນັບເປັນຜົນລວມຂອ"
"ງຄືນທີ່ແຂກແຕ່ລະຄົນພັກເຊົາ."

#. module: holiday_house
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:holiday_house.welcome_article_body
msgid "Click one of the house to book."
msgstr "ຄລິກທີ່ເຮືອນຫຼັງໃດໜຶ່ງເພື່ອຈອງ."

#. module: holiday_house
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:holiday_house.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"Click the Check in button to confirm they are now staying at your place!"
msgstr ""
"ຄລິກປຸ່ມ Check in ເພື່ອຢືນຢັນວ່າຕອນນີ້ພວກເຂົາກຳລັງພັກຢູ່ບ່ອນຂອງທ່ານແລ້ວ!"

#. module: holiday_house
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:holiday_house.welcome_article_body
msgid "Click the Check out button to capture they return you the keys."
msgstr "ຄລິກປຸ່ມ Check out ເພື່ອບັນທຶກວ່າພວກເຂົາໄດ້ສົ່ງຄືນກະແຈໃຫ້ທ່ານແລ້ວ."

#. module: holiday_house
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:holiday_house.welcome_article_body
msgid "Click the Create Order to open the order form."
msgstr "ຄລິກທີ່ ສ້າງໃບສັ່ງຈອງ ເພື່ອເປີດແບບຟອມການສັ່ງຈອງ."

#. module: holiday_house
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:holiday_house.welcome_article_body
msgid "Click the Invoice button with a full invoice."
msgstr "ຄລິກປຸ່ມ ໃບແຈ້ງໜີ້ ເພື່ອສ້າງໃບແຈ້ງໜີ້ເຕັມຮູບແບບ."

#. module: holiday_house
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:holiday_house.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"Click the Pay with demo button, and then Pay button to mimic the payment."
msgstr "ຄລິກປຸ່ມ ຊຳລະດ້ວຍຕົວຢ່າງ, ແລະ ຈາກນັ້ນປຸ່ມ ຊຳລະ ເພື່ອຈຳລອງການຊຳລະເງິນ."

#. module: holiday_house
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:holiday_house.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"Click the tail of the corresponding booking and drag it to the requested "
"date."
msgstr "ຄລິກທີ່ສ່ວນທ້າຍຂອງການຈອງທີ່ກ່ຽວຂ້ອງ ແລະ ລາກມັນໄປຫາວັນທີທີ່ຕ້ອງການ."

#. module: holiday_house
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:holiday_house.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"Configure the email delay as you wish the email to be sent after the guest "
"checkout."
msgstr ""
"ຕັ້ງຄ່າໄລຍະເວລາການສົ່ງອີເມລຕາມທີ່ທ່ານຕ້ອງການ ໃຫ້ອີເມລຖືກສົ່ງອອກຫຼັງຈາກແຂກເຊັກເອົາ."

#. module: holiday_house
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:holiday_house.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"Create a new leave selecting the appropriate working schedule, the one from "
"your stay resources."
msgstr ""
"ສ້າງການລາໃໝ່ໂດຍເລືອກຕາຕະລາງການເຮັດວຽກທີ່ເໝາະສົມ, ເຊິ່ງແມ່ນອັນດຽວກັນກັບຊັບພະຍາກອນບ່ອນພັກຂອງທ່າ"
"ນ."

#. module: holiday_house
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:holiday_house.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"Create a new leave the same way as previously, but this time specify the "
"resource this applies to."
msgstr ""
"ສ້າງການລາໃໝ່ໃນຮູບແບບດຽວກັນກັບກ່ອນໜ້ານີ້, ແຕ່ຄັ້ງນີ້ໃຫ້ລະບຸຊັບພະຍາກອນທີ່ການລານີ້ມີຜົນບັງຄັບໃຊ້."

#. module: holiday_house
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:holiday_house.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"Created offers are assigned no company nor branch (default behavior).<br/>As"
" a result, they are available from all companies and branches, as well as "
"all websites from those."
msgstr ""
"ຂໍ້ສະເໜີທີ່ສ້າງຂຶ້ນຈະບໍ່ຖືກກຳນົດໃຫ້ບໍລິສັດ ຫຼື ສາຂາໃດໜຶ່ງ (ເປັນຄ່າເລີ່ມຕົ້ນ).<br/>ສົ່ງຜົນໃຫ້ພວກມັນສາມາດໃຊ້ໄດ້ຈ"
"າກທຸກບໍລິສັດ ແລະ ສາຂາ, ລວມທັງທຸກເວັບໄຊທ໌ຂອງພວກເຂົາ."

#. module: holiday_house
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:holiday_house.welcome_article_body
msgid "Define start and end date time and save your leave."
msgstr "ກຳນົດວັນທີ ແລະ ເວລາເລີ່ມຕົ້ນ ແລະ ສິ້ນສຸດ ຈາກນັ້ນບັນທຶກການລາຂອງທ່ານ."

#. module: holiday_house
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:holiday_house.welcome_article_body
msgid "Discover more about Odoo by diving into our"
msgstr "ຄົ້ນຫາເພີ່ມເຕີມກ່ຽວກັບ Odoo ໂດຍການເຂົ້າໄປເບິ່ງໃນ"

#. module: holiday_house
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:holiday_house.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"Discover the basics of this package and explore all the possibilities Odoo "
"offers to improve your experience."
msgstr ""
"ຄົ້ນຫາພື້ນຖານຂອງແພັກເກດນີ້ ແລະ ສຳຫຼວດຄວາມເປັນໄປໄດ້ທັງໝົດທີ່ Odoo ມອບໃຫ້ເພື່ອປັບປຸງປະສົບການຂອງທ່ານ."

#. module: holiday_house
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:holiday_house.welcome_article_body
msgid "Don't forget to save your setting changes."
msgstr "ຢ່າລືມບັນທຶກການປ່ຽນແປງການຕັ້ງຄ່າຂອງທ່ານ."

#. module: holiday_house
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:holiday_house.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"During an available period, click, drag and drop on a house line to create a"
" slot."
msgstr "ໃນຊ່ວງເວລາທີ່ວ່າງ, ຄລິກ, ລາກ ແລະ ວາງໃສ່ແຖວຂອງເຮືອນເພື່ອສ້າງການຈອງ."

#. module: holiday_house
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:holiday_house.welcome_article_body
msgid "Each company can have its own website!"
msgstr "ແຕ່ລະບໍລິສັດສາມາດມີເວັບໄຊທ໌ຂອງຕົນເອງໄດ້!"

#. module: holiday_house
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:holiday_house.welcome_article_body
msgid "Employee assignations"
msgstr "ການມອບໝາຍພະນັກງານ"

#. module: holiday_house
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:holiday_house.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"Employee would open the tasks from their hand and update the status until "
"Clean."
msgstr ""
"ພະນັກງານຈະເປີດເບິ່ງວຽກຈາກມືຖືຂອງພວກເຂົາ ແລະ ອັບເດດສະຖານະຈົນກວ່າຈະກາຍເປັນ \"ສະອາດ\"."

#. module: holiday_house
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:holiday_house.welcome_article_body
msgid "Enforcing weekly turnover"
msgstr "ການບັງຄັບໃຊ້ຮອບວຽນລາຍອາທິດ"

#. module: holiday_house
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:holiday_house.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
